# calc_semantic_nested_parens.numos — two grouped factors: (2 + 3) * (4 - 1) == 15.
#
# Phase 8C semantic smoke. NO screenshot, NO golden.
#
# Exercises two independent parenthesised groups multiplied together. As in
# calc_semantic_parentheses.numos, each group is exited with RIGHT (the `)` key is
# a no-op). (2+3) * (4-1) = 5 * 3 = 15.
#
# Run: program --headless --deterministic --script <this> --frames 1400 --quiet
# Exit codes: 0 ok · 2 parse · 3 screenshot · 4 assertion failure.

log "calc_semantic_nested_parens: waiting for launcher"
wait 200
open_app Calculation
wait 60

key (
key 2
key +
key 3
key RIGHT
key *
key (
key 4
key -
key 1
key RIGHT
key ENTER
wait 120

assert_app Calculation
assert_no_error
assert_result 15
log "calc_semantic_nested_parens: PASS ((2+3)*(4-1) == 15)"
